childOf("Dependencies") is already handled in EvergreenService.initDependenciesTopic() .
GenericExternalService should only handle lifecycle scripts change.
c.subscribe((what, child) -> {
  if (child.childOf(VERSION_CONFIG_KEY)) {
    requestReinstall();
  }
  if (!child.childOf("lifecycle")) {
    return;
  }
  if (child.childOf("shutdown")) {
    return;
  }
  if (child.childOf("install")) {
    requestReinstall();
    return; 
  }
  requestRestart();
}

